OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 08 MAR
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2021FPiers Morgan's comments on ITV's
OL,7,FGood Morning Britain, that he didn't
OL,8,Fbelieve claims made by Meghan Markle
OL,9,Fabout her mental health, following the
OL,10,Finterview with the Duke and Duchess of
OL,11,FSussex, resulted in 54,595 complaints
OL,12,Fto Ofcom.
OL,13,
OL,14,FThis was the highest number of
OL,15,Fcomplaints to the regulator since 2004
OL,16,Fand whilst the on air segment didn't
OL,17,Fbreak broadcasting rules, ITV were
OL,18,Freminded to take greater care around
OL,19,Fcontent discussing mental health and
OL,20,Fsuicide.
OL,21,
OL,22,
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
